reviewText: One of my favorite movies of all time is Kindergarten Cop. Plus watching the new one is always great too.
Kindergarten cop was funny and fun to watch. our whole family really enjoyed it. The Kindergarten Cop 2 movie was good and funny, but the first one was much much better
